1. Business Objectives
Track overall sales and revenue performance
Identify top & low-performing products
Analyze regional sales trends
Measure monthly & yearly growth
Improve decision-making using KPIs

2. Dataset Description
Dataset Type: Retail Sales Data
Source: Simulated real-world business dataset

Columns Used:
Column Name	Description
Order_ID	Unique order identifier
Order_Date	Date of purchase
Customer_Name	Customer name
Product	Product name
Category	Product category
Region	Sales region
Quantity	Units sold
Unit_Price	Price per unit
Revenue	Quantity √ó Unit_Price
Payment_Mode	Cash / Card / UPI

